1. ansible (hosts group) -m setup
2. you may use above info with something like grep ipv4
3. you may also use filter on any secton using below command
4. ansible (hosts group) -m setup -a 'filter=*ipv4*' (pull anything that has ipv4 in it)
5 you may now save all those information gathered using the following command in a folder.
6. ansible (hosts group) -m setup --tree facts 
